1. *Lud* čovek je napravio veliku grešku. (The crazy man made a big mistake.) 
2. Ona je postala *luda* od očaja. (She became crazy from desperation.)
3. U njegovom ponašanju je nešto *ludo*. (There is something crazy in his behaviour.)
4. *Ludi* planovi su ga doveli u nevolju. (His crazy plans brought him into trouble.)
5. *Ludilo* se nastavlja do zore. (The craziness continues until dawn.)